# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺股票、期貨等投資市場入面，當資產價格下跌至某個預設水平時，將資產賣出，以限制虧損進一步擴大嘅行為（量詞：次）
eng:stop loss
<eg>
yue:佢設定咗止蝕位，所以雖然股價跌咗，但佢只係蝕少少就收手。 (keoi5 ding6 zung6 zo2 zi2 sik1 wai6, so2 ji1 zo1 gwa1 gaap3 dit3 zo2, daan6 keoi5 zi2 si1 sik1 siu2 siu2 zau1 sau1 syu2.)
eng:He set a stop-loss order, so although the stock price dropped, he cut his losses and exited with only a small loss. [end of text]


